Program: Outlook
Title: Revisiting Eye Witnesses to the 9/11 Attacks
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsjh
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Revisiting the woman who lived in sight of the Twin Towers in New York and who witnessed the September 11th attacks in 2001. Semantics King Junior the Liberian refugee in Ghana who became a journalist and reunited with his mother through his paper. Lorna Barrett recalls travelling by ship from USA to the UK in 1942. Revisiting the woman who went into labour in New York on 9/11. Show less